527
00:57:39,440 --> 00:57:41,829
Fred and George are the batsmen of the team.

528
00:57:42,040 --> 00:57:45,589
Our job is to protect you.

529
00:57:45,800 --> 00:57:48,360
Quidditch is a brutal game.
but no one has died in years.

530
