Before the stairs move again!

542
00:58:59,040 --> 00:59:02,316
Do you also feel,
that we should not be here?

543
00:59:02,560 --> 00:59:04,596
We MUST not be here!

544
00:59:04,800 --> 00:59:08,554
This floor is forbidden!

545
00:59:09,680 --> 00:59:11,193
Let's get out of here.

546
00:59:13,320 --> 00:59:16,073
