641
01:09:45,800 --> 01:09:50,635
If Harry and Ron hadn't come
I would probably be dead now.

642
01:09:51,600 --> 01:09:55,832
It is very possible
It was a very stupid idea!

643
01:09:56,040 --> 01:10:01,478
