644
01:10:01,680 --> 01:10:04,558
5 points deducted for Gryffindor,

645
01:10:04,760 --> 01:10:08,196
for your poor judgment.

646
01:10:08,640 --> 01:10:10,551
And you two gentlemen

647
01:10:10,760 --> 01:10:14,036
I hope you realize how lucky you were

648
01:10:14,240 --> 01:10:17,516
Not many first-year students could handle
a full-grown mountain troll

649
01:10:17,720 --> 01:10:20,234
