650
01:10:20,480 --> 01:10:22,789
5 points...

651
01:10:24,120 --> 01:10:27,112
For recklessness!

652
01:10:36,960 --> 01:10:40,555
I'm keeping watch. It might wake up.

653
01:10:48,104 --> 01:10:50,743
Have some breakfast.

654
01:10:50,944 --> 01:10:54,016
Ron is right. You need your powers today.

655
01:10:54,224 --> 01:10:56,340
I am not hungry.

656
01:10:56,904 --> 01:11:02,297
Good luck today Potter.
Now that you've dealt with a troll

