Scared, Harry?
A little.

674
01:12:45,384 --> 01:12:48,899
I was also scared before my first match.

675
01:12:49,104 --> 01:12:52,460
What happened?
I don't really remember.

676
01:12:52,744 --> 01:12:55,304
After 2 minutes I got a slap

677
01:12:55,504 --> 01:12:58,223
and woke up in hospital a week later.

678
