Hello and welcome to the first
first Quidditch match of the season.

679
01:13:22,944 --> 01:13:27,460
Match of the day:
Slytherin meets Gryffindor!

680
01:13:56,504 --> 01:13:58,859
Players take their positions

681
01:13:59,064 --> 01:14:02,693
while Mrs. Hooch starts the game!

682
01:14:02,904 --> 01:14:06,101
