even gone mad.

795
01:32:23,744 --> 01:32:27,703
Therefore, it will be moved tomorrow.

796
01:32:27,904 --> 01:32:29,735
And I must ask you
not to look for it again.

797
01:32:30,664 --> 01:32:34,373
not to look for it again.

798
01:32:35,104 --> 01:32:38,096
One should not sink into dreams

799
01:32:38,664 --> 01:32:41,417
so you forget to live

800
01:33:33,904 --> 01:33:39,342
I made you look in the wrong place.
How could I be so stupid?

801
01:33:39,584 --> 01:33:42,542
I borrowed it several weeks ago,
to have something easy to read.

802
01:33:42,744 --> 01:33:44,655
Is this "easy"?

803
01:33:49,064 --> 01:33:51,373
Here it is!

804
01:33:51,584 --> 01:33:55,418
Nikolas Flamel is the only known
creator of the Philosopher's Stone!

805
01:33:55,664 --> 01:33:56,779
What?

806
01:33:57,424 --> 01:34:00,302
Do you never read?

807
01:34:00,504 --> 01:34:04,816
"The Philosopher's Stone is a legendary substance

808
01:34:05,024 --> 01:34:07,538
that can turn metal into gold

809
01:34:07,744 --> 01:34:11,578
and produce the elixir of life,
the liquid that makes you immortal.

810
01:34:11,784 --> 01:34:13,854
Immortal?
It means that you never die.

811
01:34:14,064 --> 01:34:16,055
I know what it means!

812
01:34:16,904 --> 01:34:21,420
The only existing stone
belongs to Nicolas Flamel

813
01:34:21,624 --> 01:34:26,573
An alchemist who last year
celebrated his 665th birthday.

814
01:34:28,224 --> 01:34:30,294
That's what Fluffy is guarding.

815
01:34:30,504 --> 01:34:35,020
That is what is under the trapdoor.
The Philosopher's Stone!

816
01:34:51,104 --> 01:34:54,733
Unfortunately, I am not able to
receive guests today.

817
01:34:54,944 --> 01:34:57,538
We know the 'Philosopher's Stone'!

818
01:35:02,064 --> 01:35:06,979
