01:35:15,664 --> 01:35:18,940
I'm a bit busy now so

823
01:35:19,144 --> 01:35:21,704
Wait a minute... One of the teachers?

824
01:35:21,904 --> 01:35:25,613
Of course it is!
Other teachers protect it too

825
01:35:25,824 --> 01:35:28,338
with incantations!
Quite rightly

826
01:35:28,584 --> 01:35:31,496
A waste of time in my opinion.

827
01:35:31,704 --> 01:35:33,695
No one can get past Fluffy.

828
01:35:33,904 --> 01:35:37,419
No one knows how except
me and Dumbledore.

829
01:35:37,664 --> 01:35:41,100
I should not have told you

830
01:35:54,384 --> 01:35:59,253
Hagrid, what is that?
It's... uhh

831
01:35:59,504 --> 01:36:01,415
I know what it is!

832
01:36:01,624 --> 01:36:04,138
But Hagrid, how did you get one?

833
01:36:04,504 --> 01:36:07,621
I won it from a stranger down at the inn!

834
01:36:07,824 --> 01:36:11,737
He seemed happy to get rid of it

835
01:36:33,064 --> 01:36:35,180
Is it

