Look, look, look! He knows who his mom is.

840
01:36:49,984 --> 01:36:51,656
Hello, Norbert.

841
01:36:51,984 --> 01:36:56,102
Norbert?
He must have a name.

842
01:36:56,824 --> 01:36:59,179
Right, Norbert?

843
01:37:05,864 --> 01:37:08,856
He has to be trained a bit, of course.

844
01:37:12,584 --> 01:37:14,575
