866
01:38:46,064 --> 01:38:51,184
He has a small mission in the Dark Forest.

867
01:38:53,184 --> 01:38:56,017
Sorry about all this, Hagrid.

868
01:38:57,424 --> 01:39:02,214
You're not still thinking about
about that damn dragon?

869
01:39:04,384 --> 01:39:06,375
Norbert is gone.

870
01:39:06,904 --> 01:39:10,294
Dumbledore sent him to a
colony in Romania.

871
01:39:10,584 --> 01:39:13,701
That way he can be with his own kind.

872
01:39:13,864 --> 01:39:16,094
What if he doesn't like Romania?

873
01:39:16,304 --> 01:39:20,377
What if the other dragons are naughty?
He's just a kid, right?

874
01:39:20,984 --> 01:39:26,012
Pull yourself together, man!
You're going into the forest.

875
01:39:26,224 --> 01:39:28,499
Better get your brain working.

876
01:39:28,704 --> 01:39:34,142
