880
01:39:44,704 --> 01:39:47,264
Be sure of it.

881
01:39:49,144 --> 01:39:50,497
Natti, natti

882
01:39:52,984 --> 01:39:55,703
So let's go

883
01:40:32,344 --> 01:40:34,653
Hagrid, what is that?

884
01:40:34,864 --> 01:40:38,095
