Can you see this?

885
01:40:38,584 --> 01:40:43,738
It is unicorn blood. I found a dead
unicorn a few weeks ago.

886
01:40:44,264 --> 01:40:48,655
This one has been seriously wounded.

887
01:40:55,864 --> 01:41:01,382
So it's our job to find the poor animal.

888
01:41:01,584 --> 01:41:04,576
Ron, Hermione. You're coming with me.

889
01:41:05,024 --> 01:41:08,175
Harry, you go with Malfoy.

890
01:41:09,384 --> 01:41:11,579
But I get Faithful!

891
01:41:11,744 --> 01:41:17,262
Yes, of course. I just want you to know
he's a real coward.

892
01:41:20,784 --> 01:41:25,574
Wait till my father hears about this!
This is a job for servants!

893
01:41:25,784 --> 01:41:29,538
One might think you are afraid.

894
01:41:29,744 --> 01:41:32,212
I'm not afraid, Potter.

895
01:41:33,304 --> 01:41:35,181
Did you hear that?

896
01:41:37,624 --> 01:41:38,977
Come, Faithful

897
01:41:39,184 --> 01:41:40,617
Afraid!

898
01:42:04,584 --> 01:42:06,654
What is it Faithful?

899
01:43:14,144 --> 01:43:19,423
Harry Potter, you must go!
You are known by many creatures here.

900
01:43:19,624 --> 01:43:23,458
The forest is not safe at that time,
especially not for you.

901
01:43:23,664 --> 01:43:26,303
But what was it you saved me from?

902
01:43:26,504 --> 01:43:31,624
A terrible creature!
It is terrible to kill a unicorn.

903
01:43:31,824 --> 01:43:37,137
Drinking its blood keeps you alive,
even if you are a hair's breadth from death.

904
01:43:37,344 --> 01:43:42,213
But you pay a terrible price.
When you kill something so innocent

905
01:43:42,424 --> 01:43:47,054
the moment it touches your lips
your lips, you will have half a life.

906
01:43:47,264 --> 01:43:48,982
A life under a curse.

907
01:43:49,184 --> 01:43:52,972
Who would choose such a life?
Who do you think?

908
01:43:53,184 --> 01:43:57,939
Are you saying that what killed the unicorn

909
01:43:58,264 --> 01:44:02,018
and drank its blood
