910
01:44:02,224 --> 01:44:07,173
Do you know what is hidden here in the forest right now

911
01:44:07,984 --> 01:44:09,463
"The Philosopher's Stone"

912
01:44:10,744 --> 01:44:12,655
Harry!

913
01:44:13,224 --> 01:44:17,536
Good evening, Florence.
I see you've met young Mr. Potter.

914
01:44:17,744 --> 01:44:19,814
Are you okay, Harry?

915
01:44:20,904 --> 01:44:25,022
Harry Potter,
I'll leave you here.

916
01:44:25,864 --> 01:44:29,539
You are safe now. Good luck to you.

917
01:44:36,864 --> 01:44:40,823
You mean "You know who"
is out there in the forest?

918
01:44:41,024 --> 01:44:43,697
But he is weak. He lives on
unicorns.

919
01:44:43,904 --> 01:44:46,702
We were wrong.

920
01:44:46,904 --> 01:44:51,102
Snape doesn't want the Stone for himself,
it's for Voldemort.

921
01:44:51,304 --> 01:44:55,661
The Elixir of Life makes Voldemort strong again.

922
01:44:55,864 --> 01:44:57,377
So that he can return.

923
