But if he comes back

924
01:44:59,504 --> 01:45:03,292
You don't think he will
try to kill you, do you?

925
01:45:04,264 --> 01:45:07,654
I think he would have killed me
tonight if he had the chance.

926
01:45:07,864 --> 01:45:11,300
And I, who have only been worried
about my potions exam.

927
01:45:11,504 --> 01:45:14,940
Wait a minute, we're forgetting one thing.

928
01:45:15,304 --> 01:45:19,980
Which wizard is it that
Voldemort has always feared?

929
01:45:20,704 --> 01:45:25,619
Dumbledore. As long as Dumbledore
is around, Harry, you're safe.

930
01:45:25,824 --> 01:45:29,703
As long as Dumbledore is here,
you're safe. he won't get to you.

931
01:45:35,224 --> 01:45:40,423
I thought the Hogwarts exam would be scary,
but it was actually pretty fun.

932
01:45:40,624 --> 01:45:44,139
Speak for yourself.
Are you okay, Harry?

933
01:45:44,344 --> 01:45:49,293
My scar... it burns.
It has happened before!

934
01:45:49,504 --> 01:45:52,064
Not like this.
Maybe you should see a doctor?

935
01:45:52,264 --> 01:45:55,620
I think it's a warning.
It means that danger is coming.

936
01:46:02,944 --> 01:46:05,299
Of course it is!
What is it?

937
01:46:05,504 --> 01:46:09,099
Isn't it strange, that what Hagrid
wants most of all is a dragon

938
01:46:09,304 --> 01:46:12,262
and then a stranger shows up who just happens to have one?

939
01:46:12,464 --> 01:46:15,024
I mean, how many people walk around
around with dragon eggs in their pocket.

940
01:46:15,224 --> 01:46:17,374
Why didn't I think of that before.

941
01:46:22,744 --> 01:46:26,100
Who gave you the egg?
What did he look like?

942
01:46:26,304 --> 01:46:28,943
I don't know, he was wearing a hood.

943
01:46:29,144 --> 01:46:31,612
What were you talking about?

944
01:46:32,184 --> 01:46:35,574
He wondered what kind of animals I had.

945
01:46:35,784 --> 01:46:39,618
I said that after Fluffy,
a dragon should be no problem.

946
01:46:39,824 --> 01:46:44,102
Did he seem interested in Fluffy?
Of course he was!

947
01:46:44,504 --> 01:46:48,497
How often do you see a three-headed dog?

948
01:46:48,704 --> 01:46:54,097
I told him that the trick to dealing with
a beast like that is to know how to calm them down.

949
01:46:54,304 --> 01:46:59,537
Take Fluffy, for example.
Play him some music and he will fall asleep.

950
01:47:01,104 --> 01:47:03,698
I shouldn't have told you that...

951
01:47:03,944 --> 01:47:06,060
Where are you going?

952
01:47:12,784 --> 01:47:15,423
We need to see Professor Dumbledore, now!

953
01:47:15,864 --> 01:47:18,378
But Professor Dumbledore is not here, I'm afraid.

954
01:47:18,584 --> 01:47:22,702
