Magic Association and flew directly to London.

955
01:47:23,104 --> 01:47:25,538
Has he gone away? But it is important!

956
01:47:25,784 --> 01:47:27,900
It's about the Philosopher's Stone!

957
01:47:29,744 --> 01:47:33,293
How do you know...?
Someone is trying to steal it!

958
01:47:33,904 --> 01:47:38,898
I do not know how you know about the stone.
But I can assure you that it is safe.

959
01:47:39,104 --> 01:47:43,222
Now go back to your rooms.
Quietly and calmly.

960
01:47:51,184 --> 01:47:53,857
It was Snape that Hagrid met!

961
01:47:54,064 --> 01:47:56,624
