965
01:48:14,384 --> 01:48:17,774
Uh... We, uh...
You should be careful

966
01:48:18,304 --> 01:48:20,181
People might think that you

967
01:48:24,304 --> 01:48:26,898
is doing something.

968
01:48:36,784 --> 01:48:38,695
What do we do now?

969
01:48:38,904 --> 01:48:42,499
We go down through the trapdoor. Tonight.

970
01:48:55,704 --> 01:48:57,103
Trevor.

971
01:48:57,424 --> 01:49:00,700
Trevor, shut up! You can't be here!

972
01:49:00,944 --> 01:49:06,143
Neither can you.
You're going to sneak out again, aren't you?

973
01:49:06,344 --> 01:49:10,132
Neville listens
No you can't!

974
01:49:10,384 --> 01:49:14,775
