He has cast a spell on the harp.

985
01:50:22,144 --> 01:50:25,022
It has a horrible smell!

986
01:50:27,504 --> 01:50:29,495
We have to move his paw.
What? Uh...

987
01:50:29,704 --> 01:50:31,057
Let's go!

988
01:50:34,944 --> 01:50:36,935
Okay... hugs!

989
01:50:59,144 --> 01:51:02,614
I will go first. Do not follow until I give the signal.

990
01:51:02,824 --> 01:51:07,614
If something goes wrong,
make sure you get out!

991
01:51:08,384 --> 01:51:11,694
Hasn't it become a bit quiet?

992
01:51:12,384 --> 01:51:14,136
harp

993
01:51:14,784 --> 01:51:17,378
