994
01:51:27,024 --> 01:51:28,093
HOPE!

995
01:51:41,704 --> 01:51:45,174
Luckily, there were plants here.

996
01:51:59,024 --> 01:52:01,982
Don't move! It's the Devil's Snare.

997
01:52:02,184 --> 01:52:05,733
You have to relax...
Otherwise it will just kill us faster.

998
01:52:05,944 --> 01:52:10,734
Killing us faster?
Now I can really relax!

999
01:52:12,904 --> 01:52:14,178
Hermione!

1000
01:52:14,744 --> 01:52:18,373
What do we do now?
Just relax!

1001
01:52:18,584 --> 01:52:22,896
Hermione, where are you?
Do as I say! Trust me!

1002
01:52:29,704 --> 01:52:32,901
